description:
*** Inspect by Appointment Only ***

A substantial floor plan with dual balconies and outstanding design creates a sense of exceptional space and light in this contemporary apartment. North facing in the block, the floor plan is intelligently configured, including a generous entry hall with storage, free flowing indoor to outdoor living spaces and a private master wing complete with a stunning ensuite and its own balcony. It's a very private retreat with luxury on-trend fixtures and finishes making it an exceptional home or investment. It comes with a security car space plus storage and a prime locale meters to multiple bus services and steps to local cafes, Mowbray Public School and Lane Cove's vibrant village hub.

- A great investment opportunity with immediate rental income
- Just leased out for $770 per week (12 months agreement till December 2023)
- Spacious open plan living and dining areas, ducted a/c
- Contemporary flooring, generous entertainer's alfresco balcony
- Luxury stone and gas kitchen, large island bench, quality appliances
- Private master wing with ensuite, robes and private balcony
- Large 2nd bedroom with robes and access to main balcony
- Two stylish bathrooms, spacious storage wall, concealed laundry
- Quality 'Ariana' boasts security intercom entry and lift access
- Single security car space plus storage cage
- Within the Chatswood High school and Mowbray Public catchments
- Moments walk to bus services, Mowbray Public and Lane Cove village hub
- Unit size 103 sqm + 15 sqm car space & storage
- Strata rates approx. $1,127 pq


For more information, please visit www.rwayrealtychatswood.com
